The '''Restful Nights Hotel''' was reputed to be anything but. Located on [[Faldos]], it was supposed to be a haven for people who did not want to be found, but its employees had a tendency to take up the [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] trade when the mood struck them.

